data.description: Move right into this Immaculate two story condo at Lifestyle Communities Falls at Hayden Run. Condo is an end unit, offering additional windows, light, and hardwood floors. Kitchen includes beautiful upgrades including granite, under mount sink, pantry and stainless steel appliances. Large two story great room w/ fireplace. Bright sun room and large first floor owners suite offering dual vanities, walk in closet, and separate shower/soaking tub. Upstairs includes two large bedrooms with HUGE walk in closet and Jack&Jill bathroom w/ dual vanity. Open loft great for office or additional seating. Offers an oversized two car attached garage. As a resident, enjoy the OM fitness center w/ free classes, pools, The Goat, resident events, & much more!
